        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/images/img1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Hero Image 1">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Welcome to <span style="color: #f9d423">SketchSphere</span></h1>
                    <p>Discover our exclusive collection of handcrafted artworks that bring your imagination to life</p>
                    <a href="/shop" class="btn">Explore Collection</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/img1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Hero Image 2">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Artistic <span style="color: #ff4e50">Excellence</span></h1>
                    <p>Where creativity meets craftsmanship - find the perfect piece that speaks to your soul</p>
                    <a href="/shop" class="btn">Shop Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/img1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Hero Image 3">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Creative <span style="color: #f9d423">Inspiration</span></h1>
                    <p>Transform your space with our carefully curated collection of timeless masterpieces</p>
                    <a href="/shop" class="btn">View Gallery</a>
